    <title>National Climate Service Corps and Careers Network Act of 2021</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the National and Community Service Act of 1990 to establish a National Climate Service Corps to help communities withstand and respond to changes in the Earth's climate with respect to natural disasters, and for other purposes.</title>
